name: Anish Kshatriya
text: Great service, tasty pizza, but way too pricey. Almost $20 for a small pie?!

name: Amber Haden
text: This place usually has great pizza but Saturday the vegetables were old, looked and tasted like yesterdays leftovers that were left in a hot car. I have been here many times and had better pizza, if not for that I would have given a lower ratting.

name: Melissa Burke Santone
text: The employees here were very accommodating. I really enjoyed my visit.

name: Andrea Kohler
text: Made a mistake when ordering my pizza on the website and they fixed with no problem and went out of their way to make it right.  I highly recommend this Round Table Pizza. Very, very good service and as always,  excellent food.

name: Rolando Banzon, Jr.
text: The round table is not there any more. It's VONS

name: Amy Jacobe
text: I grew up on Round Table Pizza, it's hard to beat. The service her is great and pizza is wonderful.

name: killerdr3w 222
text: Dustin is the best at costumer service, ready to go the extra mile!

name: Dudu ULLOA
text: Kinda pricey, considering other local chain pizzerias. But it's fresh and they deliver, so sometimes it's worth it

name: Ariba Usman
text: Their pizza is delicious and the toppings look so fresh

name: Miss Jessica
text: Always cheery, always friendly, always great food. Thank You!

name: Andrea S
text: Best out of all chain pizza places.

name: MovingPictures Mikeyfranklin
text: The best pizza I promise you!!! Justin is the man!!!!

name: Esau Rodriguez
text: Ordered pizza with a 2 litter soda deliver guy was nice enough to get a bag of ice with the soda as well its the little things that count appreciated it
